data.description: Discover the beauty of this spacious and oversized raised ranch, offering 3-5 bedrooms and 2 full baths. This home also features Hardwoods, central air, granite countertops in the bathrooms,  and a kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, beautiful granite countertops and stainless appliances. Open the slider doors off the kitchen to access a welcoming deck, creating a seamless indoor-outdoor experience. Recently painted, with a new roof and upgraded 200-amp electrical service, this home combines modern updates with practicality. As you step into the fenced-in yard,  you'll find an ideal setting for entertaining with a pool, recently added hot tub and patio.  Enjoy the added convenience of a central location, providing easy access to shopping, dining, parks, and more. Don't miss the opportunity to make this recently refreshed raised ranch your home! Call today for your private showing!
